old.desc:
**Delivery app for emergency pharmaceutical products**

When someone is unable to leave the house, they can use the delivery app to get their medicine at home. The app would behave like any other delivery app. However, this would happen for medicine that you can purchase without prescription. If you need prescription, the doctor could register that into your account for you to order. This is specifically useful since it can take a lot of time to arrange with a pharmacy to deliver medicine or to change the medicine.

‌

The focus will be on security since it contains a lot of sensitive data. We want to have an open API to connect multiple chains. In the sense that, we build an API and would leave the possibilities for pharmacies to connect to it open. Based on the outcome of the state of the art, the management methodology will be decided and ideas for the security surrounding the storage of the personal data.
